      • connectTarget

        public final void connectTarget(ObjectTarget<BaseMessage> target)
                         throws Exception
        Description copied from interface: ObjectSourceAsync
        Connects a target to this source. This method returns immediately. All data that becomes available in this source will be passed to an Absorb.Target instance passed to this method. Target will be closed when this source is exausted. Target will remain connected till this source is exhausted or target will indicate no more interest via false result of one of absorbation method calls. Throws IllegalStateException if this source already has a target connected to it.
